verbose_text: However, a more significant decrease was only observed in the two long-term treatment groups as compared to the two short-term treatment groups (P < 0.05, SHRSP-Los16 vs. SHRSP-Los6; P < 0.05, SHRSP-Aml16 vs. and SHRSP-Aml6), although SHRSP-Los6 was more effective in reducing AT1R levels than SHRSP-Aml6 (# P < 0.05).
